metadata.name: Forgotten people
metadata.description:
Forgotten people

This art piece reflects all the forgotten ones that despite being in the streets, society turned them invisible.
All the ghost ones that after a misfortune disappeared in front of our very eyes. 
This could be you, me, some relative, or your neighbor, we never know what life reserve for us and for that reason we need to be grateful for what we have right now.

A tribute to all the invisible ones.
